  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Sales Engineer",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Responsible for identifying, negotiating and maximising new business opportunities.</p></li><li><p>Maintain good relationships with existing customers.</p></li><li><p>Attend tender site shows, assess site conditions and prepare tender proposals.</p></li><li><p>Analysis of market growth potential and competition of assigned products and systems.</p></li><li><p>Develop sales and marketing plans and strategies for products and systems in different markets based on market analysis and customer feedback.</p></li><li><p>Conceptualise and generate technical write-ups, publication articles and white papers for product promotional purposes.</p></li><li><p>Work closely with Technical and Project teams to provide solutions to customers.</p></li><li><p>Maintain sound technical and application knowledge in assigned products and systems</p></li><li><p>Deliver product training and presentations to internal teams and customers</p></li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Minimum 3-years' experience sales or business development in Industrial loT, Control & Automation</p></li><li><p>Degree or diploma in engineering, IT or relevant qualifications.<br /></p></li></ul><p><strong>HOW TO APPLY:</strong></p><p>Interested applicants, kindly send your resume in MS WORD format or please click on “Apply Now”.</p><p>We regret only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p><p>Important Note: Trust Recruit Pte Ltd is committed to safeguarding your personal data in accordance with the Personal Data Protection Act (PDPA).</p><p>Please read our privacy statement on our corporate website.</p><p>Trust Recruit Pte Ltd</p><p>EA License No: 19C9950</p><p>EA Personnel: Tan Sin Yong (Stella)</p><p>EA Personnel Reg No: R24124127</p>",
